body_html:
I have very similar issue:

Have I written custom code No
OS Platform and Distribution WIN10 Visual Studio 2015
TensorFlow installed from stable release v1.10.1
Bazel version 0.17.2
CUDA/cuDNN version CUDA8.0 / CUDNN 7.0
GPU model and memory 1050Ti / 8G
Mobile device N/A
Exact command to reproduce
bazel build -c opt //tensorflow/tools/lib_package:libtensorflow
ran after python ./configure.py

I have tried the script located in
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/tools/ci_build/windows/libtensorflow_gpu.sh --- the GPU version. Ended again after a long build with similiar error. Whole bunch of Eigen and protobuf errors.

**TensorFlow installed from** stable release v1.10.1
**Bazel version** 0.17.2
**CUDA/cuDNN version** CUDA8.0 / CUDNN 7.0
**GPU model and memory** 1050Ti / 8G
**Mobile device**  N/A
**Exact command to reproduce**
 bazel build -c opt //tensorflow/tools/lib_package:libtensorflow
ran after python ./configure.py

I have tried the script located in
